# Dashboard Route Guidance

- Prioritize "percentage to close" visibility across project lists and detail pages.
- Keep checklist actions fast: edit, add, delete, and mark ready-for-client with clear feedback.
- Ensure verified vs pending deliverables are easy to scan with consistent status semantics.
- Preserve a strong publish gate so client-facing handoff only occurs after agency review.
- Keep dashboard pages compositional and avoid embedding complex domain logic directly in view files.
